Job Description:
-Analyze and evaluate the evolution of marketing 
 environment, competition, client’s needs, satisfaction and 
 complaints, and other marketing intelligence for a 
 development and improvement of products & services;
-Work closely with relevant sales channels to ensure proper 
 and timely execution of all activities and     promotions;
-Monitor competitor’s market intelligence, benchmarking 
 against competitors and global industry practices;
-Developing the marketing strategy for the company in line 
 with company objectives;
-Manage website and social media such as: Facebook, 
 Instagram, Youtube etc. ; 
-Manage, arrange and overseeing the company’s marketing 
 budget;
-Creation and publication of all marketing material in line 
 with marketing plans;
-Planning and implementing promotional campaigns with 
 suppliers and agencies; 
-Overall responsibility for company branding awareness and corporate identity;
-Monitor and report on effectiveness of marketing 
 communications;
-Analyzing potential strategic partner relationships for 
 company marketing;
 Other tasks assigned by supervision.

Job Requirement:
-Master’s or Bachelor’s degree in marketing, management, 
 business administration or others related fields;
-At least 5 years solid experiences in marketing management 
 with multi-businesse of company; 
-Have a good interpersonal skill, hardworking, and honesty;
-Having a good communication skills and creative idea;
-Strong leadership, organizational, problem solving and 
 influencing skills;
-Dynamic and pleasant personality;
-Fluent in both written and spoken English;
-Computer literacy in Microsoft office, Internet, E-mail, 
 Outlook.

